content: I've been going to the one at Rutgers for years, I'm so glad they opened one in Hoboken. I always get their carne asada tacos with extra beans. I definitely recommend.

Toast X Bowl is SO good!! I get myself a caramel frappe with extra whipped cream everytime I go... and I got alot! The staff is super friendly and the food is really good as well. Definitely one of my favorite spots in Hoboken
